&lt;h2 id=&quot;ren-sheng-zhe-xue&quot;&gt;人生&#x2F;哲学&lt;a class=&quot;zola-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#ren-sheng-zhe-xue&quot; aria-label=&quot;Anchor link for: ren-sheng-zhe-xue&quot;&gt;🔗&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
