&lt;li&gt;&lt;a rel=&quot;noopener nofollow noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.paulgraham.com&#x2F;hackernews.html&quot;&gt;我从 Hacker News 中学到了什么？&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
